Bola Bamigbola, Osogbo The driver of a commercial bus and a passenger were Saturday evening abducted by gunmen along near Wasinmi Village, along Ife-Ibadan Expressway. According to sources, immediately after the incident happened, police operatives at a checkpoint close to the scene of the crime engaged the abductors in an exchange of gunfire. READ ALSO: Blachowicz beats Adesanya to retain heavyweight title But the abductors were said to have escaped through the bush with two people. The spokesperson of Osun Police Command, Yemisi Opalola, confirmed the incident, saying operatives had been deployed to the scene of the crime. She also said three suspects had been arrested. Details shortlyâ€¦